    private static String encoded = " 000000000000000000000000!001000100010000000100000#010101110101011101010000$001000110110001101100010&001001010011010101110000(001001000100010000100000)010000100010001001000000*010100100111001001010000+000000100111001000000000,000000000000000001100100-000000000111000000000000.000000000000000000100000/0001000100100100010000000001101010101010101100000100100110001000100111000020110000100100100011100003011000010010000101100000400010101011100010001000050111010001100001011000006001001000110010100100000701110001001100100010000080010010100100101001000009001001010011000100100000:000000000010000000100000<000100100100001000010000=000000000111000001110000>010000100001001001000000?011000010010000000100000@[011001000100010001100000]011000100010001001100000^001001010000000000000000_000000000000000000001111`{001100100110001000110000|001000100010001000100000}011000100011001001100000~010110100000000000000000";

    public static void draw(Engine engine, int x, int y, String text, Color color) {
        for (int i = 0; i < text.length(); i++)
            draw(engine, x + 4 * i, y, text.charAt(i), color);
    }

    private static void draw(Engine engine, int x, int y, char c, Color color) {
        int pos = encoded.indexOf(c);
        for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
            for (int j = 1; j <= 4; j++)
                if (encoded.substring(i * 4 + j + pos, i * 4 + j + 1 + pos).equals("1"))
                    engine.setPixel(x + j, y + i, color);

    }

